Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:29.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想試著談場猜謎般的戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:32.03,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:40.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:45.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.88,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:54.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.19,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.60,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:24.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做夢嗎？現在的夢還不能說！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.34,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.00,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:40.09,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎樣的天氣 I need you!!
